/#
   A type describing the principal exchange features of the return swap.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.PrincipalExchangeFeatures {
  # The true/false flags indicating whether initial, intermediate or final exchanges of principal should occur.
  principalExchanges : FpML5.confirmation.PrincipalExchanges?

  # Specifies each of the characteristics of the principal exchange cashflows, in terms of paying/receiving counterparties, amounts and dates.
  principalExchangeDescriptions : FpML5.confirmation.PrincipalExchangeDescriptions

}

principalExchanges.Doc: The true/false flags indicating whether initial, intermediate or final exchanges of principal should occur.
principalExchanges.Name: principalExchanges

principalExchangeDescriptions.Doc: Specifies each of the characteristics of the principal exchange cashflows, in terms of paying/receiving counterparties, amounts and dates.
principalExchangeDescriptions.Name: principalExchangeDescriptions
